{"tid":2136433,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不「國際」很好嘛！──李純恩","createTime":"2020-08-02T06:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T07:31:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76c6caa826c2c0c8af14f5b21d1ddc978417f667","tid":2136433,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/KGRSEUUJQFEZNNOFQINWNRCYYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FKGRSEUUJQFEZNNOFQINWNRCYYI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=36fd6df1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FKGRSEUUJQFEZNNOFQINWNRCYYI%2F&h=1063cad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/KGRSEUUJQFEZNNOFQINWNRCYYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不「國際」很好嘛！──李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YMMin8I5T01tD2ol5LNKQ_K9M18=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BYAGOFHWQ5F25OBQR6EVSLKKOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYMMin8I5T01tD2ol5LNKQ_K9M18%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBYAGOFHWQ5F25OBQR6EVSLKKOU.jpg&h=2eaaac4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李純恩fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭宣佈暫停跟香港的逃犯引渡條例那天，我那位胸懷祖國放眼世界的北京朋友，一如既往打電話來聊國際大事，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我老實告訴他，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n北京朋友覺得找一個香港人來說香港跟外國的引渡條例非常切題，不料我毫不關心，他覺得有點掃興，於是加重語氣說，你知道嗎，這是「國際關係」的大事！我不懂國際關係，但知道什麼是「國際」。於是跟他說，所謂「國際關係」，先要有「國際」對不對？如果沒有「國際」，就沒有「國際關係」了對不對？但現在你看看，美國、英國、加拿大、澳洲、新西蘭還有歐盟，加上印度，加上南中國海那一圈，甚至東亞的日本，都在「搬起石頭砸自己的腳」，不是跟香港斷逃犯引渡條例，就是禁什麼「抖音」「微信」，爭先恐後跟中國過不去。為什麼呢？當然是因為中國太強大了嘛。現在中國「強大得」斷六親，不「國際」了。不「國際」，就沒有「國際關係」的負擔，不用討人喜歡，不用看人臉色，關起門來吃飯，說一不二，輕鬆愉快，多開心呀！我叫北京朋友凡事要用正能量看待，做人要positive；「國際關係」這樣看，才一片光明嘛！他聽了，說再去研究研究，就收綫了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5167c6554f0e68b4693436581221423c51082e","tid":2136433,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e08f9555eb3e64ed8dd0d8437ed762cda1a118","tid":2136433,"uid":357033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6e5f6d4268ce3cff6a2d805b853aabc71b6c04","tid":2136433,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b600ddb6847f604db8261da6f8251ec672e7efa","tid":2136433,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}